<h3>FAQ Help</h3>

<p>
The Frequently Asked Questions module allows you to maintain a list
of comment questions that area asked on your site. Whether they are
asked on the discussion forums, through article comments or poll
comments doesn't matter.  The purpose is to collect all of the common
questions into organized documents so your readers can easily find
answers to their questions.
</p>

<p>
It is common on the Internet to abbreviate this feature FAQ and you
will see this used throughout the site.
</p>

<p>
You are not limited to creating a single FAQ document.  You can create
multiple documents each with an introduction, summary and an entire
set of questions.  You can order the FAQ documents however you like and
also order the FAQ questions to suit your needs.
</p>

<!-- SECTION_END:Overview -->

