<h3>FAQ Questions Help</h3>

<p>
The FAQ Questions are the heart of the Frequently Asked Questions module.
They contain all of the common questions asked by visitors to your ASP Nuke
site.  Questions are grouped together by documents and you must indicate
the document you want to work with before you start editting the questions.
</p>

<p>
I like to organize my questions so that the most commonly asked questions
appear at the top of the list.  You can always add the questions first and
reorder them later using the <i>up</i> and <i>down</i> links in the question
list.  You may also want to put the novice (beginner) questions at the top
of the list to help newcomers.
</p>

